rows.label: bf02370100_0020
rows.name: Not so fast, my dear intruders.

rows.label: bf02370100_0030
rows.name:
Letting a terrorist from Iira out of my grasp
would make me look very bad indeed.

rows.label: bf02370100_0040
rows.name:
Ah, that emerald Core Crystal!
You must be the Holy Grail!

rows.label: bf02370100_0050
rows.name:
Much as it pains me to admit it,
it seems Meleph was right on the money.

rows.label: bf02370100_0060
rows.name:
You know about Homura? 
Are you after her too?

rows.label: bf02370100_0070
rows.name: Watch your mouth. But well, obviously.

rows.label: bf02370100_0080
rows.name:
The most powerful Blade in all of history,
with the power to rend Alst asunder?

rows.label: bf02370100_0090
rows.name:
Only a fool would know of that power
and not seek to claim it!

rows.label: bf02370100_0110
rows.name: Therefore, I will claim her as my own!

rows.label: bf02370100_0120
rows.name: You cannot argue with such logic!

rows.label: bf02370100_0130
rows.name: Flaw detected in final step of logic.

rows.label: bf02370100_0140
rows.name:
Too bad - neither I nor Homura 
are going to be your trophy.
